model.name: Miao2010 - Innate and adaptive immune responses to primary Influenza A Virus infection_1_1

body.div: Model 2 of the Miao et. al. 2010 is curated. Model 1 is attached as additional file.

div.p: This model is hosted on BioModels Database and identified by: BIOMD0000000546.
